data.description: Beautiful 3 bed 2.1 bath home in the heart of Avoyelles. Some inside features include tray ceilings in the living area, kitchen and bedrooms. There is also recessed lighting throughout the home, multiple bedrooms with Jack and Jill bathrooms with the master bath having a whirlpool tub, stall shower and two walk-in closets. The kitchen opens up to a huge living area. This home is in excellent condition and will qualify for 100% financing with approved credit.
